# Animal-detection-using-ML-and-Deep-Learning


## Description
This project classifies animals using machine learning and deep learning techniques.

## Tech Stack
- Python
- TensorFlow / Keras
- OpenCV
- Google Colab

## Features
- Image classification of animals
- Model training and evaluation
- Predicts animal from input image

## How to Run
1. Open notebook in Google Colab
2. Upload dataset
3. Run all cells
